38:35.581 --> 38:37.583
- YOU EXPECT TOO MUCH, MEL.

38:37.616 --> 38:39.851
- WHAT?

38:39.885 --> 38:42.087
- I SAID YOU EXPECT TOO MUCH.

38:42.120 --> 38:44.055
- THAT MY SISTER
COULD AT LEAST ACKNOWLEDGE

38:44.089 --> 38:45.491
THE BIRTH OF OUR SON?

38:45.524 --> 38:47.426
- OF ME.

38:47.459 --> 38:49.094
YOU WANT ALL MY TIME,
MY DEVOTION,

38:49.127 --> 38:52.864
AND IF YOU DON'T GET IT,
YOU THINK WE HAVE A PROBLEM.

38:52.898 --> 38:54.966
YOU GET ANGRY THAT I SEE
THE BABY MORE THAN YOU.

38:55.000 --> 38:56.134
YOU BLAME ME BECAUSE BRIAN

38:56.167 --> 38:57.536
WOULDN'T GIVE YOU
PARENTAL RIGHTS.

38:57.569 --> 38:58.637
I SUPPOSE IT'S EVEN MY FAULT

38:58.670 --> 39:00.105
THAT I CAN HAVE A CHILD
AND YOU CAN'T.

39:00.138 --> 39:02.073
- HEY, THAT'S NOT FAIR.

39:02.107 --> 39:05.110
- I FEEL LIKE I SPEND HALF
MY LIFE APOLOGIZING TO YOU,

39:05.143 --> 39:09.781
TRYING TO CONVINCE YOU
THAT I LOVE YOU.

39:09.815 --> 39:13.485
ONLY NOTHING'S EVER ENOUGH.

39:13.519 --> 39:15.954
I'M STARTING TO WONDER
IF ANYTHING EVER COULD BE.

39:22.994 --> 39:25.497
- [sighs]

39:32.871 --> 39:36.141
WELL, I ASKED YOU TO TALK,
AND YOU DID.

39:45.050 --> 39:48.053
[dance music]

39:48.086 --> 39:55.727
*

39:55.761 --> 39:59.665
- [groans]

39:59.698 --> 40:03.969
I TELL YOU, HANGING WITH BRIAN
IS EXHAUSTING.

40:04.002 --> 40:06.572
BUT IT'S WORTH IT
FOR THE SEX.

40:06.605 --> 40:08.640
- YOU'RE HAVING SEX
WITH BRIAN?

40:08.674 --> 40:10.476
- OF COURSE NOT.

40:10.509 --> 40:12.110
WE HAVE SYMBIOSIS.

40:12.143 --> 40:14.746
- OH, MY GOD.
IS THERE ANYTHING THEY CAN DO?

40:14.780 --> 40:16.181
YOU MUSTN'T GIVE UP HOPE.

40:16.214 --> 40:17.783
- IT'S NOT A DISEASE,

40:17.816 --> 40:20.018
IT'S A PERFECT RELATIONSHIP.

40:20.051 --> 40:21.753
YOU KNOW, LIKE, UH,

40:21.787 --> 40:24.890
THE YELLOW TICKBIRD
AND THE RHINOCEROS.

40:24.923 --> 40:27.593
THE YELLOW TICKBIRD
FEEDS ON PARASITES

40:27.626 --> 40:30.195
ON THE RHINO'S SKIN,
AND IN TURN,

40:30.228 --> 40:32.898
THE RHINO IS WARNED
OF IMPENDING DANGER

40:32.931 --> 40:35.233
WHEN THE TICKBIRD FLIES AWAY.

40:35.266 --> 40:39.237
SIMILARLY, I SUPPLY BRIAN

40:39.270 --> 40:41.239
WITH AN OBJECT
OF SCORN AND RIDICULE,

40:41.272 --> 40:43.041
NAMELY MYSELF,

40:43.074 --> 40:45.577
AND HE SUPPLIES ME

40:45.611 --> 40:48.680
WITH UNWANTED TICKS,
UH, TRICKS.

40:48.714 --> 40:50.849
- YOU'RE DOING THIS
FOR CASTOFFS?

40:50.882 --> 40:54.553
- WELL, IN BED,
YOU CAN'T TELL.

40:54.586 --> 40:57.589
THEY'RE AS GOOD AS NEW.

40:57.623 --> 41:03.094
- TED, HAVE YOU EVER
ASKED YOURSELF...

41:03.128 --> 41:06.031
"IS--IS GOING TO TEA DANCES
WITH BRIAN

41:06.064 --> 41:08.900
"AND HAVING INDISCRIMINATE SEX
WITH COUNTLESS STRANGERS

41:08.934 --> 41:11.236
REALLY THE LIFE I WANT?"

41:11.269 --> 41:14.239
- I HAVE.
AND THE ANSWER IS,

41:14.272 --> 41:17.943
"YOU BET YOUR ASS IT IS."

41:17.976 --> 41:18.810
- HAVE YOU--
HAVE YOU EVER WONDERED,

41:18.844 --> 41:21.580
"IS THIS THE LIFE
GOD WANTS FOR ME?"

41:21.613 --> 41:25.216
- WELL, I SUPPOSE
IN HIS INFINITE WISDOM,

41:25.250 --> 41:29.287
HE DECIDED SOMEBODY
HAD TO LIVE IN PITTSBURGH.

41:29.320 --> 41:33.692
- HAVE YOU EVER WONDERED,
"IS--IS THERE A BETTER LIFE?"

41:33.725 --> 41:35.794
- YEAH.

41:35.827 --> 41:39.865
I COULD HAVE A 10-INCH DICK
AND LOOK LIKE HIM.

41:39.898 --> 41:44.169
- WELL, WHO WOULDN'T
WANT THAT?

41:44.202 --> 41:47.172
[techno music]

