THIS IS NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

42:21.907 --> 42:25.076
- YEAH, HE SAID THAT WHENEVER
YOU FEEL SAD OR UPSET,

42:25.110 --> 42:27.245
THIS IS WHERE YOU COME.

42:27.278 --> 42:29.781
THAT JUST BEING AROUND
ALL THESE COMICS

42:29.815 --> 42:34.185
BRINGS THE LIGHT
INTO YOUR EYES.

42:34.219 --> 42:35.987
- HE SAID THAT?

42:36.021 --> 42:37.923
- I GUESS HE KNOWS YOU
PRETTY WELL.

42:37.956 --> 42:42.694
- WELL, HE DOESN'T
KNOW ME ANYMORE.

42:42.728 --> 42:43.929
- YEAH.

42:43.962 --> 42:48.667
THAT IS WHY HE GOT YOU THIS.

42:48.700 --> 42:51.236
- I TOLD HIM ALREADY,
I DON'T WANT HIS CRUMMY PRESENT.

42:51.269 --> 42:54.706
- WAIT!

42:54.740 --> 42:57.342
HE MISSES YOU.
HE'S MISERABLE WITHOUT YOU.

42:57.375 --> 42:59.878
- WELL, GOOD,
HE DESERVES TO BE.

42:59.911 --> 43:01.780
- HE LOVES YOU.

43:01.813 --> 43:03.114
HE'LL NEVER ADMIT IT,
BUT HE DOES.

43:03.148 --> 43:04.215
- BRIAN--
- YOU KNOW THAT.

43:04.249 --> 43:06.818
- BRIAN DOESN'T LOVE ANYONE.

43:06.852 --> 43:09.721
HE DOESN'T BELIEVE IN LOVE,
REMEMBER?

43:09.755 --> 43:11.890
- YOU'RE THE EXCEPTION.

43:11.923 --> 43:15.894
THAT'S WHY HE HURT YOU,
SO YOU'D GO BACK WITH DAVID.

43:15.927 --> 43:17.829
HE KNEW IF HE DIDN'T, YOU'D BE
WAITING FOR HIM FOREVER.

43:17.863 --> 43:20.666
- THAT'S BULLSHIT.

43:20.699 --> 43:25.070
- THIS WAS HIS WAY
OF SAYING GOOD-BYE.

43:25.103 --> 43:27.639
- WE'VE GOT SOME NEW
FRIENDS TO MEET TONIGHT,

43:27.673 --> 43:30.241
WHOSE DARK WORLD
IS ABOUT TO BE ILLUMINATED.

43:30.275 --> 43:33.111
AND AFTERWARDS, I INVITE
YOU ALL TO GATHER IN THE FOYER

43:33.144 --> 43:35.380
AND HAVE
SOME INCREDIBLE BROWNIES

43:35.413 --> 43:38.383
BAKED BY MY INCREDIBLE WIFE.

43:38.416 --> 43:44.189
SO, LET'S GET STARTED.

43:44.222 --> 43:46.725
- HI. I-I'M DON.

43:46.758 --> 43:48.860
all: HI, DON.

43:48.894 --> 43:51.863
- UM, HOW I GOT HERE
IS A LONG STORY,

43:51.897 --> 43:56.134
BUT THAT DOESN'T MATTER
BECAUSE I'M HERE.

43:56.167 --> 43:58.770
I'VE SEEN THE LIGHT.
- GREAT.

43:58.804 --> 44:04.142
[applause]

44:04.175 --> 44:06.311
- HI, I'M EMMETT.

44:06.344 --> 44:08.279
all: HI, EMMETT.

44:08.313 --> 44:12.718
- AND I, UH, I JUST WANT
TO SAY THAT...

44:12.751 --> 44:14.853
