45:03.234 --> 45:05.170
WANT A BEER?
- HOW MANY HAVE YOU HAD?

45:05.203 --> 45:07.372
- A FEW.
- TOO MANY.

45:07.405 --> 45:12.210
- KEEP TRACK OF THE DOCTOR,
NOT ME.

45:12.243 --> 45:14.312
- I NEVER THANKED YOU
FOR MY GIFT.

45:14.345 --> 45:15.413
- YOUR GIFT?

45:15.446 --> 45:18.249
- YOUR WARD TRACKED ME DOWN,
INSISTED THAT I TAKE IT.

45:18.283 --> 45:21.219
- YEAH, WELL, I'LL HAVE
TO PUNISH HIM SEVERELY.

45:21.252 --> 45:23.421
- IT'S THE NEATEST THING
I EVER GOT.

45:23.454 --> 45:26.191
- I THOUGHT SO.

